re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"妨礙司法公正有咩問題？用遊蕩罪告晒所有調查者就唔驚啦<br />\n<br />\n執法部門侚私枉法"},{"pid":"f7fd5f9eaebe8e68a6e83ce99708056c86ce745a","tid":1994672,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"體現獅子山精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bf2eefce5c3328978d143f0feb4bc1dd7f346b","tid":1994672,"uid":83683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:43:58.000Z","msg":"發現呢個新聞cctvb係唔會報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02b0dca8d1b525c3e05004bbf55ad2ef5bfe215","tid":1994672,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:45:07.000Z","msg":"擺明衰撚左 唔揚得"},{"pid":"dca6c0fa0a91aa67150b60592421fe90cae3062e","tid":1994672,"uid":71090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:51:56.000Z","msg":"香港人真係慘到爆"},{"pid":"ad75c15360ee497d817360f59c843dcde338cad2","tid":1994672,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:52:26.000Z","msg":"點解同831唔同, 唔響法院拎"},{"pid":"e448007b33c08f260b3abd05557edf9e3a0775d0","tid":1994672,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T02:16:14.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"a3aa7b198af9396d06da11342d6930928b5f0d55","tid":1994672,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:22:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"371e7012edb9ac8ab9bfe3f920dd8457d40b4ba8","tid":1994672,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949097c3b04d52d20d986bdf4f6c235e101d80e2","tid":1994672,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im